parts.text:
```json
{
"application": "EukBook",
"software_requirements": [
"MinIO client",
"Git",
"Miniconda",
"Snakemake",
"EukRep",
"MetaEuk",
"Mailutils"
],
"resource_requirements": [
"MinIO secret file (MinIO_secret.sh)",
"EukBook repository (https://github.com/dembra96/EukBook.git)",
"Miniconda installer (https://repo.continuum.io/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh)",
"MetaEuk installer (https://mmseqs.com/archive/d49cd731e4241abfae11004b0d6da5cf3c515297/metaeuk-linux-avx2.tar.gz)"
],
"other_requirements": [
"SLURM job scheduler",
"OpenStack cloud",
"Internet connection"
],
"notes": [
"This script uses a MinIO secret file (MinIO_secret.sh) to configure the MinIO client.",
"The script uses a Snakemake configuration file (samples_small.yaml) to predownload conda packages for the EukBook pipeline.",
"The script uses a success stamp file (STAMP_$(hostname)_config_success) to indicate successful installation on the master node."
]
}
```
